Kathañca, doṇa, brāhmaṇo mariyādo hoti? 
Idha, doṇa, brāhmaṇo ubhato sujāto hoti—
mātito ca pitito ca, saṁsuddhagahaṇiko, yāva sattamā pitāmahayugā akkhitto anupakkuṭṭho jātivādena. 
